            "unidentified": "",
            "value": "<p>This staff is tapered at the base and carved into a gem-studded twist at the top. While wielding the staff, you gain a +2 circumstance bonus to checks to identify evocation magic.</p>\n<p><strong>Activate</strong> Cast a Spell</p>\n<p><strong>Effect</strong> You expend a number of charges from the staff to cast a spell from its list.</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Cantrip</strong> @Compendium[pf2e.spells-srd.Ghost Sound]{Ghost Sound}</li>\n<li><strong>1st</strong> @Compendium[pf2e.spells-srd.Illusory Disguise]{Illusory Disguise}, @Compendium[pf2e.spells-srd.Illusory Object]{Illusory Object}</li>\n<li><strong>2nd</strong> @Compendium[pf2e.spells-srd.Illusory Creature]{Illusory Creature}, @Compendium[pf2e.spells-srd.Item Facade]{Item Facade}</li>\n<li><strong>3rd</strong> @Compendium[pf2e.spells-srd.Illusory Disguise]{Illusory Disguise}, @Compendium[pf2e.spells-srd.Item Facade]{Item Facade}</li>\n<li><strong>4th</strong> @Compendium[pf2e.spells-srd.Illusory Creature]{Illusory Creature}, @Compendium[pf2e.spells-srd.Veil]{Veil}</li>\n<li><strong>5th</strong> @Compendium[pf2e.spells-srd.Illusory Scene]{Illusory Scene}, @Compendium[pf2e.spells-srd.Veil]{Veil}</li>\n<li><strong>6th</strong> @Compendium[pf2e.spells-srd.Hallucination]{Hallucination}, @Compendium[pf2e.spells-srd.Mislead]{Mislead}</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Craft Requirements</strong> Supply one casting of all listed levels of all listed spells.</p>\n<hr />\n<p>Automatically applied effects:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>+2 circumstance bonus to checks to identify illusion magi</li>\n</ul>"
